title: Electricity prices for households in Belgium 2010 - 2019 , semi-annually
summary: In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has rose over the Year.
Euro cents per kilowatt-hour is roughly constant from 2014_S1 to 2014_S2, and lastly slightly increasing from 2014_S2 to 2016_S1.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015_S1 and 2015_S2.
The highest Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, of value 25.44 was reached at Year 2016_S1
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 20.43 was reached at Year 2014_S2
